### Dota 2 Modding Disclaimer

ArdysaModsTools is a tool designed to assist with modding Dota 2 by modifying game files. Please be aware that modding Dota 2 may violate the terms of service or end-user license agreement (EULA) of Dota 2 and/or Steam, as set by Valve Corporation. Using this tool to modify Dota 2 game files is at your own risk. The author(s) and contributors of ArdysaModsTools are not responsible for any consequences, including but not limited to account bans, data loss, or game instability, that may result from using this tool. Always back up your Dota 2 game files before applying mods, and ensure compliance with Valve's policies.
